# BondMaster Architecture Rules

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15+
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui
- Supabase
- PostgreSQL
- Vercel

## Standards
- Strict TypeScript
- Server Actions
- Zod validation
- React Query
- RBAC
- Row Level Security
- Audit logs
- Responsive UI
- Dark mode

## Folder Structure
/app
/components
/modules
/lib
/hooks
/actions
/store
/types

## Naming
- Components: PascalCase
- Hooks: useXxx
- Server actions: verbNoun
- DB tables: snake_case
